      <div class="panel-heading">
        <h3 class="panel-title bold">Personal Change <span class="label label-danger">Step 1</span></h3>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-quote">
        <quote>"Be the change you want to see in the world." &mdash; Gandhi</quote>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-body">
        <p>The fate of the world is decided by the billions of tiny actions and decisions that each of us performs every single day. In order to transform this world, we - as individuals - must start by changing ourselves. We must become conscious citizens. We must become aware of the intricate links and consequences that our actions are having on the world. And we must gain an understanding of the great challenges of our time and must identify their core reasons.<br/><br/>
        
          In the first stage, Neonia will become a resource hub for changing our personal lives. From business to banking to the enviroment to all other elements of our day-to-day interactions - Neonia will compile information on the current standard practices, raise awareness of the associated problems and consequences, and provide alternatives so that each of us can start making a difference right now.</p>
      </div>
