        <h3 class="panel-title bold">Systemic Change <span class="label label-danger">Step 2</span></h3>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-quote">
        <quote>"The secret of change is to focus all of your energy, not on fighting the old, but on building the new." &mdash; Aristotle</quote>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-body">
        <p>The problems that we see on our planet - poverty, malnutrition, environmental exploitation - are systemic. They are the direct consequences of the societal, economic, and political systems that we operate the world on. Systems putting financial profits above anything, creating hierachies of political power, and fostering cultures of individualism and competition.<br/><br/>
        
        It is time to invent a new generation of societal, economic, and political systems. Systems that put humanity and nature first, that distribute political power equally among each of us, and that create a mindset of community and collaboration. Systems that allow every human being to thrive and to follow their heart.<br/><br/>
        
        To do so, we will build Neonia - a global, borderless, online country dedicated to empowering every human being to flourish. We will implement our own decision-making processes, our own rules for a new economic system, and we will foster a culture based on community and collaboration.</p>
      </div>
