        <h3 class="panel-title bold">Global Change <span class="label label-danger">Step 3</span></h3>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-quote">
        <quote>"When injustice becomes law, resistance becomes duty." &mdash; Thomas Jefferson</quote>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-body">
        <p>
        We live in a world in which the current status quo is competition, wealth inequality, and environmental exploitation. In which the place of one's birth and one's socio-economic status determine so greatly the opportunities of one's future. In a world in which a majority of people are denied their full potential.
          
          <br/><br/>When poverty, malnutrition, war, and environmental exploitation are as widespread and systemic as they are today, it is not enough to change ourselves and to build an alternative system. In this world, it is our duty and responsibility to rise up for our fellow human beings. Rising up not in violent riots, but in raising awareness, seeking solutions, and implementation-focused collaboration.
          
          <br/><br/>Neonia will work towards a wholely flourishing planet Earth by empowering all of us to change the communities within which we live. Together, we will shift our planet from the world we have to the world we want: world peace, humans thriving in harmony with nature, no individual's prosperity based on the withering of another, everyone free to individually choose the government system they wish to live under. Together, we will write the future of humanity.
        
        </p>
